    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Rails的關連小筆記]]></title>
    <link href="http://hechien.github.com/octopress/blog/2012/02/02/railsde-guan-lian-xiao-bi-ji/"/>
    <updated>2012-02-02T16:04:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://hechien.github.com/octopress/blog/2012/02/02/railsde-guan-lian-xiao-bi-ji</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今天在<a href="http://rails-bestpractices.com">rails best practices</a>中看到一則<a href="http://rails-bestpractices.com/posts/80-active-record-query-interface-optimization">ActiveRecord Query Interface Optimization</a>，裡面提到在<code>has_many</code>與<code>belongs_to</code>的時候可以自訂<code>:select</code>來指定要撈出的欄位 &#8230; 所以請繼續閱讀</p>

<!-- more -->


<p>後來我發現這個方式很適合用在類似需要<code>Record.includes(:user)</code>的時候，因為<code>User</code>的欄位可能過多且資料量太大導致就算打了index也跑不快，所以用這種方式來撈可以加速 &#8230; 因此我便寫了</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>record.rb </span></figcaption>
 <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='rb'><span class='line'><span class="n">belongs_to</span> <span class="ss">:user</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="nb">select</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="ss">:id</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>可是後來發現這樣會沒辦法在事後加上欄位，所以在需要特定欄位的時候必須另外寫一個自訂的關連</p>

<figure class='code'><figcaption><span>record.rb </span></figcaption>
 <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='rb'><span class='line'><span class="n">belongs_to</span> <span class="ss">:user_with_udid</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">{</span><span class="nb">select</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="o">[</span><span class="ss">:id</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="ss">:udid</span><span class="o">]</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">class_name</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="s2">&quot;User&quot;</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">foreign_key</span><span class="p">:</span> <span class="ss">:user_id</span><span class="p">}</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<p>這樣子一來，就能夠用以下方式取得UDID了
<code>Record.includes(:user_with_udid).last.udid</code></p>
]]></content>
